#, kde-format
msgid "DC shift"
msgstr "Posun DC"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:7
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply a DC shift to the audio.\n"
"This can be useful to remove a DC offset (caused perhaps by a hardware "
"problem in the recording chain) from the audio.\n"
"The effect of a DC offset is reduced headroom and hence volume. The astats "
"filter can be used to determine if a signal has a DC offset."
msgstr ""
"Použije DC posun na zvuk.\n"
"Toto môže byť užitočné na odstránenie DC ofsetu (spôsobeného možno "
"hardvérovým problémom v nahrávacom reťazci) zo zvuku.\n"
"Efektom DC ofsetu je znížená rezerva a teda hlasitosť. Filter astats možno "
"použiť na zistenie, či má signál DC ofset."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:11
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the DC shift, allowed range is [-1, 1]. It indicates the amount to shift "
"the audio."
msgstr ""
"Nastaviť jednosmerný posun, povolený rozsah je [-1, 1]. Určuje množstvo "
"posunutia zvuku."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Limiter gain"
msgstr "Nárast limitéra"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Optional. It should have a value much less than 1 (e.g. 0.05 or 0.02) and is "
"used to prevent clipping."
msgstr ""
"Voliteľné. Malo by mať hodnotu oveľa menšiu ako 1 (napr. 0,05 alebo 0,02) a "
"používa sa na zabránenie orezávania."

