msgid "Yaw"
msgstr "Vybočenie"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:10
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:10
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount to rotate the image<br>\n"
"    \t(nose moves from side to side)."
msgstr ""
"Množstvo otočenia obrazu<br>\n"
"    \t(nos sa pohybuje zo strany na stranu)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:13
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:11
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "Pitch"
msgstr "Výška tónu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:15
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount to rotate the image<br>\n"
"    \t(nose up or down)."
msgstr ""
"Množstvo otočenia obrazu<br>\n"
"    \t(nos nahor alebo nadol)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:18
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:14
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "Roll"
msgstr "Náklon"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:20
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount to rotate the image<br>\n"
"    \t(clockwise or anticlockwise rotation along the axis of movement)."
msgstr ""
"Množstvo otočenia obrazu<br>\n"
"    \t(otočenie v smere alebo proti smeru hodinových ručičiek pozdĺž osi "
"pohybu)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:23
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "FOV"
msgstr "Zorné pole"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The horizontal field of view, in degrees, of the resulting frame.<br>\n"
"    \tAny value over 179 results in a fisheye projection."
msgstr ""
"Horizontálne zorné pole výsledného snímku v stupňoch.<br>\n"
"    \tAkákoľvek hodnota nad 179 má za následok projekciu typu rybieho oka."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:28
#, kde-format
msgid "Fisheye"
msgstr "Rybí oko"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:30
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount of fisheye to mix in.<br>\n"
"    \t100 means that you get a 100% fisheye lens."
msgstr ""
"Množstvo efektu rybieho oka na primiešanie.<br>\n"
"    \t100 znamená, že dostanete 100% objektív rybieho oka."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Equirectangular to Stereo"
msgstr "VR360 ekvidistantné na stereo"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Projects a stereographic image from an equirectangular. Use this to create "
"the little planet effect from a VR360 footage."
msgstr ""
"Premieta stereografický obraz z ekvirektangulárneho. Použite na vytvorenie "
"efektu malej planéty zo záberov VR360."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:24
#, kde-format
msgid "Nearest-neighbor,Bilinear"
msgstr "Najbližší sused,Bilineárne"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Wrap"
msgstr "VR360 zabalenie"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Stretches a section of the equirectangular panorama to cover the entire VR "
"sphere"
msgstr "Natiahne časť ekvirektangulárneho panorámy na pokrytie celej VR sféry"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid "Determines the sampling method"
msgstr "Určuje metódu vzorkovania"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:14
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:18
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:22
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:26
#, kde-format
msgid "Degrees from the center of the image to keep unchanged"
msgstr "Stupne od stredu obrazu, ktoré zostanú nezmenené"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:29
#, kde-format
msgid "Blur start"
msgstr "Začiatok rozmazania"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Horizontal fraction of the unchanged area to blur over in the equator band"
msgstr "Horizontálny zlomok nezmennej oblasti na rozmazanie v pásme rovníka"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "Blur end"
msgstr "Koniec rozmazania"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "Horizontal fraction of the unchanged area to blur over at the poles"
msgstr "Horizontálny zlomok nezmenenej oblasti na rozmazanie na póloch"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Hemispherical to Equirectangular"
msgstr "VR360 hemisférické na ekvidistantné"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Converts a video frame with two hemispherical images to a single "
"equirectangular frame. The plugin assumes that both hemispheres are in the "
"frame"
msgstr ""
"Skonvertuje video snímku s dvoma hemisférickými obrazmi na jednu "
"ekvirektangulárnu snímku. Doplnok predpokladá, že obe hemisféry sú v snímke"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Alignment yaw"
msgstr "Zarovnanie horizontálneho otočenia"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:10
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:15
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The two fisheye cameras of a 360 camera are rarely perfectly 180 degrees "
"apart.<br>\n"
"    \tThese parameters adds a rotation to both lenses to correct for this."
msgstr ""
"Dve kamery s rybím okom 360° kamery sú zriedka presne 180 stupňov od seba."
"<br>\n"
"    \tTieto parametre pridávajú rotáciu obom objektívom na korekciu tohto "
"rozdielu."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "Alignment pitch"
msgstr "Zarovnanie výšky tónu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "Alignment roll"
msgstr "Zarovnanie náklonu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "Projection"
msgstr "Projekcia"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:24
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The fisheye projection type. Currently only equidistant fisheyes, like the "
"Ricoh Theta and Garmin Virb360 are supported."
msgstr ""
"Typ projekcie rybieho oka. V súčasnosti sú podporované iba ekvidistantné "
"rybie oká, ako napríklad Ricoh Theta a Garmin Virb360."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid "Equidistant Fisheye"
msgstr "Ekvidistantné rybí oko"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:28
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens FOV"
msgstr "Zorné pole objektívu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:29
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The field of view of a single hemisphere in degrees, expressed as a fraction "
"of the frame width."
msgstr ""
"Zorné pole jednej hemisféry v stupňoch, vyjadrené ako zlomok šírky snímky."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:32
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens radius"
msgstr "Polomer objektívu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The radius of the image circle, expressed as a fraction of the frame width."
msgstr "Polomer obrazového kruhu, vyjadrený ako zlomok šírky snímky."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:36
#, kde-format
msgid "Front X"
msgstr "Predná X"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:38
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the front-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe X parameter is a fraction of the image width."
msgstr ""
"Stred obrazu a orientácia obrazu pre kameru smerujúcu dopredu.<br>\n"
"    \tParameter X je zlomok šírky obrazu."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:41
#, kde-format
msgid "Front Y"
msgstr "Predná Y"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:43
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the front-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe Y parameter a fraction of the image height."
msgstr ""
"Stred obrazu a orientácia obrazu pre kameru smerujúcu dopredu.<br>\n"
"    \tParameter Y je zlomok výšky obrazu."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:46
#, kde-format
msgid "Front Up"
msgstr "Predná hore"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:48
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the front-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tUp is the \"up\" direction in the image, in degrees clockwise from a "
"direction towards the frame top edge."
msgstr ""
"Stred obrazu a orientácia obrazu pre prednú kameru.<br>\n"
"    \tHore je smer „hore“ v obraze, v stupňoch v smere hodinových ručičiek "
"od smeru k hornému okraju snímky."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:51
#, kde-format
msgid "Back X"
msgstr "Späť X"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:53
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the back-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe X parameter is a fraction of the image width.."
msgstr ""
"Stred obrazu a orientácia obrazu pre zadnú kameru.<br>\n"
"    \tParameter X je zlomok šírky obrazu."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:56
#, kde-format
msgid "Back Y"
msgstr "Späť Y"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:58
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the back-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe Y parameter a fraction of the image height."
msgstr ""
"Stred obrazu a orientácia obrazu pre kameru smerujúcu dozadu.<br>\n"
"    \tParameter Y je zlomok výšky obrazu."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:61
#, kde-format
msgid "Back Up"
msgstr "Zálohovanie"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:63
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the back-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tUp is the \"up\" direction in the image, in degrees clockwise from a "
"direction towards the frame top edge."
msgstr ""
"Stred obrazu a orientácia obrazu pre kameru smerujúcu dozadu.<br>\n"
"    \tHore je smer \"nahor\" v obraze, v stupňoch po smere hodinových "
"ručičiek od smeru k hornému okraju snímky."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:66
#, kde-format
msgid "Nadir radius"
msgstr "Polomer nadiru"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:68
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:73
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"360 cameras like the Theta have a problem with the nadir direction where, no "
"matter what, you will have a little of the camera in the image.<br>\n"
"    \tThis parameter \"stretches\" the image near nadir to cover up the "
"missing parts."
msgstr ""
"360-stupňové kamery ako Theta majú problém so smerom nadiru, kde bez ohľadu "
"na všetko bude mať v obraze trochu kamery.<br>\n"
"    \tTento parameter „natiahne“ obraz blízko nadiru, aby zakryl chýbajúce "
"časti."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:71
#, kde-format
msgid "Nadir start"
msgstr "Začiatok nadiru"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:76
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion A"
msgstr "Skreslenie objektívu A"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:78
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:83
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:88
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lens distortion correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tThe first three parameters are the same as in Hugin."
msgstr ""
"Parametre korekcie skreslenia objektívu.<br>\n"
"    \tPrvé tri parametre sú rovnaké ako v Hugin."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion B"
msgstr "Skreslenie objektívu B"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:86
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion C"
msgstr "Skreslenie objektívu C"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:91
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion radius"
msgstr "Horizontálne"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:93
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lens distortion correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tIf you use Hugin parameters, the Radius should be set to the value of "
"(0.5 * min(image width, image height) / image width). For a 2:1 aspect dual "
"hemispherical image, that would be 0.25."
msgstr ""
"Lens distortion correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tIf you use Hugin parameters, the Radius should be set to the value of "
"(0.5 * min(image width, image height) / image width). For a 2:1 aspect dual "
"hemispherical image, that would be 0.25."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:96
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting A"
msgstr "Vinetácia objektívu A"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:98
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:103
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:108
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:113
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lens vignetting correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tThe first four parameters are the same as in Hugin, corresponding to "
"the Va, Vb, Vc and Vd image parameters."
msgstr ""
"Parametre korekcie vignety objektívu.<br>\n"
"    \tPrvé štyri parametre sú rovnaké ako v programe Hugin a zodpovedajú "
"parametrom Va, Vb, Vc a Vd."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:101
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting B"
msgstr "Vinetácia objektívu B"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:106
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting C"
msgstr "Vinetácia objektívu C"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:111
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting D"
msgstr "Vinetácia objektívu D"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:116
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting radius"
msgstr "Polomer vinetácie objektívu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If you use Hugin parameters, the radius should be set to the value of (0.5 * "
"image diagonal / image width).<br>\n"
"    \tFor a 2:1 aspect dual hemispherical image, that would be 0.5590. Use "
"the A parameter to scale the effect and avoid overexposing highlights"
msgstr ""
"If you use Hugin parameters, the radius should be set to the value of (0.5 * "
"image diagonal / image width).<br>\n"
"    \tFor a 2:1 aspect dual hemispherical image, that would be 0.5590. Use "
"the A parameter to scale the effect and avoid overexposing highlights"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:121
#, kde-format
msgid "Use sensor response parameters"
msgstr "Použiť parametre odozvy senzora"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:122
#, kde-format
msgid "Switch on to use sensor response parameters (EMoR h(x))"
msgstr "Zapnúť na použitie parametrov odozvy senzora (EMoR h(x))"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:125
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(1)"
msgstr "EMoR h(1)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:127
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:132
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:137
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:142
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Sensor response parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tThe EMoR h(x) parameters are the same as Hugin's Ra - Re in the lens "
"parameters. If you use Hugin-derived values for vignetting correction, you "
"should also use these parameters, as Hugin's vignetting correction assumes "
"that the sensor response has been corrected."
msgstr ""
"Parametre odozvy senzora.<br>\n"
"    \tParametre EMoR h(x) sú rovnaké ako Ra - Re v parametroch objektívu "
"Hugin. Ak používate hodnoty odvodené z Hugin na opravu vignetácie, mali by "
"ste tieto parametre tiež použiť, pretože oprava vignetácie Hugin "
"predpokladá, že odozva senzora bola opravená."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:130
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(2)"
msgstr "EMoR h(2)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:135
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(3)"
msgstr "EMoR h(3)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:140
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(4)"
msgstr "EMoR h(4)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(5)"
msgstr "EMoR h(5)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_rect_to_eq.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Rectilinear to Equirectangular"
msgstr "VR360 rectilineárne na ekvidistantné"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_rect_to_eq.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Converts a rectilinear (a normal-looking) image to an equirectangular image. "
"Use this together with Transform 360 to place \"normal\" footage in a 360 "
"movie."
msgstr ""
"Skonvertuje rektilíny (normálne vyzerajúci) obraz na ekvirektangulárny "
"obraz. Použite spolu s Transform 360 na umiestnenie normálnych záberov do "
"360-stupňového filmu."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Stabilize"
msgstr "VR360 stabilizovať"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:6
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Stabilizes 360 footage.<br>\n"
"    The plugin works in two phases - analysis and stabilization. When "
"analyzing footage, it detects frame-to-frame rotation, and when stabilizing "
"it tries to correct high-frequency motion (shake)."
msgstr ""
"Stabilizuje 360° záznamy.<br>\n"
"    Zásuvný modul pracuje v dvoch fázach – analýza a stabilizácia. Pri "
"analýze záznamu detekuje rotáciu medzi snímkami a pri stabilizácii sa pokúša "
"opraviť vysokofrekvenčný pohyb (tras)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid "Analyze"
msgstr "Analyzovať"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:10
#, kde-format
msgid "Switch on for analysis phase; switch off for stabilization phase."
msgstr "Zapnúť pre fázu analýzy; vypnúť pre fázu stabilizácie."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "Motion analysis file"
msgstr "Súbor analýzy pohybu"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Select the file to store stabilization data in"
msgstr "Vyberte súbor na uloženie dát stabilizácie"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "Start offset"
msgstr "Počiatočný posun"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The offset into the stabilization file that corresponds to the start of this "
"clip.<br>\n"
"    \tFor example, if you have a 30 second clip, analyze it all, and then "
"split it into three clips of 10 seconds each, then the start offsets should "
"be 0s, 10s, and 20s."
msgstr ""
"Posun v stabilizačnom súbore, ktorý zodpovedá začiatku tohto klipu.<br>\n"
"    \tNapríklad ak máte 30-sekundový klip, analyzujete ho celý a potom ho "
"rozdelíte na tri 10-sekundové klipy, počiatočné posuny by mali byť 0 s, 10 s "
"a 20 s."

